ey.readObject(...)`\n  - reaches `ObjectInputStream#readObject()`\n\nIt also verifies the restored key preserves algorithm, format, parameter spec, encoded private/public key bytes, equality, and hash code.\n\nPer instruction, I did not run tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ca487b5e2b5a627016a261e0dd7e88190ab47a2bcf320984f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2230, "output": 800, "cacheRead": 36864, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 39894, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780882942849, "responseId": "resp_0ca487b5e2b5a627016a261dff7a4c81908ab814f2f451381e"}}
